== 制作 ==
[[File:the_town_affleck_hamm.JPG|thumb]]与[[乔·汉姆|乔·汉姆]]在马萨诸塞州[[剑桥_(马萨诸塞州)|剑桥]]的拍摄场地闲谈的情景]]
制作始於2009年8月底，地点是在[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]][[波士顿|波士顿]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bostonherald.com/track/inside_track/view.bg?articleid=1194574 |title=Ben Affleck, Blake Lively are the talk of ‘The Town’ |last1=Gayle |first1=Fee |last2=Raposa |first2=Laura |date=2009-09-01 |work=Boston Herald |accessdate=2009-09-05 |archive-date=2012-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120813052343/http://news.bostonherald.com/track/inside_track/view.bg?articleid=1194574 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.bostonherald.com/track/inside_track/view.bg?articleid=1194574 |title=Blake Gets a Baby Welcome to Ben's Town |author=PopSugar |date=2009-09-01 |work=PopSugar |accessdate=2009-09-05 |archive-date=2012-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120813052343/http://news.bostonherald.com/track/inside_track/view.bg?articleid=1194574 |dead-url=no }}</ref>过去的MASSBank分行位於[[梅尔罗斯_(马萨诸塞州)|梅尔罗斯]]，被用作电影场景中的银行，并命名为Cambridge Merchants Bank。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wickedlocal.com/melrose/fun/entertainment/arts/x366050607/Melrose-Lights-cameras-action-in-city-as-Ben-Affleck-movie-shoots-locally-this-month |title=Melrose: 'Lights, cameras, action' in city as Ben Affleck movie shoots locally this month |last=DeMaina |first=Daniel |date=2009-10-09 |work=Melrose Free Press |publisher=GateHouse Media |accessdate=2009-10-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120131231417/http://www.wickedlocal.com/melrose/fun/entertainment/arts/x366050607/Melrose-Lights-cameras-action-in-city-as-Ben-Affleck-movie-shoots-locally-this-month |archivedate=2012-01-31 }}</ref>剧组也在康涅狄格州{{link-en|安卡斯维尔|Oxoboxo River}}的{{link-en|金神大赌场|Mohegan Sun}}中拍摄赌场中的情景，并在马萨诸塞州{{link-en|沃尔波尔 (马萨诸塞州)|Walpole, Massachusetts|沃尔波尔}}的MCI-Cedar Junction监狱中拍摄监狱的接访室。

== 反响 ==
这部电影在美国评论界得到了一致好评。电影在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]上获得了94%的正面评价，基於214條評論，平均分為7.7/10，[[IMDb|IMDb]]评分达到7.6分（满分10分）。评论家们特别赞赏了[[班·艾佛列克|班·艾佛列克]]在抢劫场景之中的執導手法。在影评人{{link-en|A·O·史考特|A. O. Scott}}在《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》中所写的评论中，他如此评论影片开始的抢劫场景：“这一场景如同电影中其他大多数动作片段一样的紧凑、残酷和高效，证实了班·艾佛列克作为导演的技巧和自信。”<ref>Scott, A.O. [http://movies.nytimes.com/2010/09/17/movies/17town.html?ref=movies&pagewanted=all Bunker Hill to Fenway: A Crook’s Freedom Trail] {{Wayback|url=http://movies.nytimes.com/2010/09/17/movies/17town.html?ref=movies&pagewanted=all |date=20130603153528 }}, New York Times (2010年9月16日).</ref>

一些评论家评论说这部电影与[[迈克尔·曼|迈克尔·曼]]的电影《[[盗火线|盗火线]]》（Heat）惊人的相似，认为情节和风格实际上是相同的，Laremy Lengel甚至将他发表於《[[西雅图邮讯报|西雅图邮讯报]]》的文章命名为《The Town Works Best if You Avoid the Heat》。<ref>Lengel, Laremy. [http://www.seattlepi.com/movies/426872_film40895315.html "The Town Works Best if You Avoid the Heat"], Seattle Post Intelligencer (September 17, 2010).</ref>

[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]对这部电影给出了3星（满分4星），赞赏了[[杰瑞米·雷纳|杰瑞米·雷纳]]的表演和本·阿弗莱克的导演手法。

